<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَلِعُمْرَةٍ:</span> مِنَ الحِلِّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَيَصِحُّ مِنْ مَكَّةَ، وَعَلَيْهِ دَمٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَسُنَّ لِمُرِيدِ الإِحْرَامِ -وَهُوَ نِيَّةُ النُّسُكِ-:<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> غُسْلٌ أَوْ تَيَمُّمٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَتَنَظُّفٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَتَطَيُّبٌ فِي بَدَنٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَكُرِهَ فِي ثَوْبٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَلُبْسُ إِزَارٍ وَرِدَاءٍ أَبْيَضَيْنِ نَظِيفَيْنِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> بَعْدَ تَجَرُّدِ ذَكَرٍ عَنْ مَخِيطٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٦]</span> وَإِحْرَامُهُ عَقِبَ صَلَاةِ فَرْضٍ، أَوْ رَكْعَتَيْنِ نَفْلًا فِي غَيْرِ وَقْتِ نَهْيٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَنِيَّتُهُ شَرْطٌ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَأَفْضَلُ الأَنْسَاكِ التَّمَتُّعُ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهُوَ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> أَنْ يُحْرِمَ بِالعُمْرَةِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> فِي أَشْهُرِ الحَجِّ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>